OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fmainly dry through the evening with
OL,7,Fjust the odd shower. Rain becoming
OL,8,Fmore persistent for a time overnight
OL,9,Fbefore further dry spells and a few
OL,10,Fshowers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FIt will be mainly dry and
OL,13,Fmild with variable cloud and some
OL,14,Fbright or sunny spells, but the chance
OL,15,Fof the odd light shower. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
