OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FOften
OL,6,Fdry with bright spells and variable
OL,7,Fcloud on Sunday but cloudier with some
OL,8,Frain later. Cloudier Monday with rain
OL,9,Fat times. Mainly dry and bright
OL,10,FTuesday, but somewhat cooler.
